data.description: Location, Location, location! Sellers have listed below market value and are ready for offers and negotiations! This ranch style just needs a little TLC to make it your dream home. Situated in the heart of Greenbrier just minutes from shopping, restaurants and interstates. 4 bedrooms and 2 full baths with a large family room and dining area located in the heart of the home. The 4th bedroom is the ROG equipped with closet and storage area. Backyard is fenced and would make a great space for family and friends to gather.
